Spring-Fill Crinkle Cut
Crinkle Cut™ shred requires no fluffing and manipulating. In one clean motion, a gift packer grabs the appropriate amount of shred and fills up the container. Speaking of clean, that's another great benefit: since you don't need to pull at it to puff it out, Crinkle Cut™ shred creates little-to-no dust, leading to a better workplace and happy gift packers.

column3: Home|Supplies & Equipment|Tape and Tape Dispensers
column4:
Definite Length Tape Dispenser

The Tach-It Model #5000 definite length tape dispenser is perfect for applications where a fixed 1½ inch length of tape is needed. Usable with 1½ wide roll or 2 individual 3/4 inch wide rolls, by simply turning the large knob the model 5000 applies the tape to a star wheel for easy removal. Perfect for gift wrap, retail, and industrial applications where a 1½ inch piece of tape is required, the Model #5000 also has a separate free mandrel for 3/4 inch tape with unlimited lengths.
